We'd like you to meet <b>Flame</b>, our Featured Citizen of the Week!<br><br>Flame has been hanging out at his <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/home/?user=10chips"><a href='/home/?user=10chips'>88612-C Timberwolf Way</a></a> pad since September 12th, 2008. He loves Metro Park and likes to take advantage of being in the middle of all the action.<br><br>Speaking of action: in the short time that Flame has lived in Millsberry, he's managed to snag an impressive collection of trophies. All totaled, he has 10 trophies ranging from the Peabody Park Half-Pipe to Sink Three. <br><br>Flame describes himself as very alert, a little curious, and shy. It seems as though he's put his alertness to good use winning trophies for both Solver and Sudoku. <br><br>Red, green, and gold just so happen to be Flame's favorite colors. Looks like someone is going to be ready for the holidays a bit early this year. <br><br>If you're trying to track Flame down, you'll probably want to check the Tree House, the Pizza Place, or the Soccer Game. He's pretty much a regular at these local hot spots.<br><br>When he's not hanging out around town or racking up trophies, Flame likes to kick back with some of his favorite tunes. If you want to join him for some jams, be sure to bring along some Rap, Pop, or Soft Rock. <br><br>So the next time you see Flame, make sure you congratulate him and thank him for being such a great citizen!<br></div>
